.remember/

# === FINAL/ workspace: GRACE Modal sweep + report deliverables ===
# Non-redistributable competition data (organizer-provided + derived merges/backups)
FINAL/IberLEF_GRACE/
FINAL/GRACE_2026_blind_test/
